how do i get a forwarding only email account stanford answers stanford university stanford answers how do i get a forwarding only email account categories accounts and ids administrative applications anti virus and security computer operating systems connecting to the network desktop hardware and support email and calendar help desk restricted information on it services software at stanford stanford hospital and clinics telephones and cable tv unix systems and software web services user login login with your sunet id home how do i get a forwarding only email account search this site a departmental or group email account is an imap group mailbox that can be shared by multiple users each user using his or her own sunet id and password to connect to the mailbox a forwarding only account defines an stanford edu address just like a departmental email account but email sent to that address is forwarded to another address such as a list you need at least one forwarding email address for a forwarding account if you have more than three addresses please create a mailing list to get a forwarding only account complete the form on the departmental email account request page be sure to set the account type to forwarding address see the group imap accounts page for requirements charges and setup information associated with group accounts departmental email accounts stanford university 450 serra mall stanford california 94305 650 723 2300 terms of use copyright complaints
